data.description: Introducing 751 Brittany Ct. A Prime Home nestled in the heart of Stone Mountain. This 3-bedroom, 2-bath newly updated home with a eat-in kitchen featuring stainless steel appliance pkg, granite countertops, ample cabinetry. Perfect for the cooking enthusiast. This one literally checks all the boxes. Just right for the picky buyer. The spacious bright & airy living room features tiled flooring and fireplace. Perfectly located. It's a stone's throw away from Hwy 78, the Village of Stone Mountain, shopping & transportation. The fenced backyard is highlighted by a stand alone shed. Wow! What A Deal!
